formdata.value: iPhone SE is the most powerful 11.94-cm (4.7) iPhone ever. It features the incredibly-fast A13 Bionic for incredible performance in apps, games, and photography, Portrait mode for studio-quality portraits and six lighting effects, Next-generation Smart HDR for incredible detail across highlights and shadows, Cinematic-quality 4K video, and all the advanced features of iOS. With long battery life and water resistance, it’s so much of the iPhone you love, in a not-so-big size.
